title: My Teacher Is An Alien Series (Bruce Coville)
description:
Okay, so maybe no one cares except me, but these books were fantastic reads when I was a kid. I had to do a bit of hunting to find e-copies of the entire series, but if anyone would like to revisit a childhood favorite, give the 'My Teacher' series a read. And if you never read them... I weep for your misspent youth. 

Contents:

My Teacher Is An Alien
My Teacher Fried My Brains
My Teacher Glows In The Dark
My Teacher Flunked The Planet
